ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectFederal Grants to assist dairy producers
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food, pursuant to subsection 12(5) of the FARM INCOME PROTECTION ACT, to provide up to $1.75 billion in federal transfer payments to compensate supply managed dairy producers for income lost as a result of the ratification of the Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-pacific Partnership and the Canada-European Union Comprehensive eeonomic and Trade Agreement.
